snippet.title: Hollywood At The High Court Amber Heard Arrives With Girlfriend Bianca Butti For Face-Off
snippet.description:
Hollywood At The High Court Amber Heard Arrives With Girlfriend Bianca Butti For Face-Off
Hollywood at the High Court: Amber Heard arrives with girlfriend Bianca Butti for face-off with estranged husband Johnny Depp as three-week libel trial begins over claims he beat her
Johnny Depp's ex-wife Amber Heard has arrived at the High Court in London for the start of a three-week libel showdown. Depp is suing The Sun newspaper and its executive editor Dan Wootton over the allegations of...
